00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:43.662
But part of my job was
being a salesperson.

00:02:43.662 --> 00:02:45.120
And what I would
do is I would walk

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:48.710
into these meetings with
a deck and with a team.

00:02:48.710 --> 00:02:52.990
But my job was to sell
that team to the investors.

00:02:52.990 --> 00:02:55.062
And in return, they
would give us money,

00:02:55.062 --> 00:02:56.270
and we would give them stock.

