So I've added a couple
things to this talk

00:03:46.640 --> 00:03:52.310
about putting together your
business plan spreadsheet.

00:03:52.310 --> 00:03:55.260
And one of them is talking
about the venture capital

00:03:55.260 --> 00:03:59.610
perspective, and helping
you sit it in their shoes

00:03:59.610 --> 00:04:03.120
and evaluate your opportunity.

00:04:03.120 --> 00:04:09.100
But also thinking about the
other uses or takers of equity

00:04:09.100 --> 00:04:09.830
in your company.

