in North Dakota for $250,000

00:57:49.070 --> 00:57:49.660
a year.

00:57:49.660 --> 00:57:52.050
Therefore, that's what
I need to pay myself.

00:57:52.050 --> 00:57:54.550
So that's kind of
an extreme case.

00:57:54.550 --> 00:57:56.520
But think about what
your peers are making,

00:57:56.520 --> 00:57:58.590
and generally you
can argue that that's

00:57:58.590 --> 00:58:00.280
what you ought to be paid.

00:58:00.280 --> 00:58:02.420
Or what you were getting
paid in your prior life,

00:58:02.420 --> 00:58:05.460
