01:05:54.820 --> 01:05:59.520
So for like your programmers,
put in $2,000 per person,

01:05:59.520 --> 01:06:00.020
per month.

01:06:00.020 --> 01:06:03.800
It sounds like a lot, but I've
worked in a couple technology

01:06:03.800 --> 01:06:07.780
companies, and it could
be an oscilloscope,

01:06:07.780 --> 01:06:11.090
