could be some CAD software.

01:06:11.090 --> 01:06:13.940
Whatever it is, these guys can
figure out a way to spin it.

01:06:13.940 --> 01:06:16.870
If that sounds like too much
to you, put in $1,000 a month.

01:06:16.870 --> 01:06:19.710
But the beauty of that is that,
as you change your staffing

01:06:19.710 --> 01:06:23.679
plan, this number just ramps
up and down in line with that.

01:06:23.679 --> 01:06:25.970
So you can make dramatic
changes to your staffing plan,

01:06:25.970 --> 01:06:29.465
you don't have to come back
here and fat-finger anything in.

01:06:29.465 --> 01:06:31.590
But some of these things,
you are going to have to,

01:06:31.590 --> 01:06:33.030
especially in the
marketing area.

01:06:33.030 --> 01:06:36.310
You're going to have to decide,
what trade shows do I go to,

01:06:36.310 --> 01:06:42.040
and what am I going to
do for sales expenses?

01:06:45.520 --> 01:06:48.910
And then you could
even put in commissions

01:06:48.910 --> 01:06:52.300
in here, commissions as
a percentage of sales,

01:06:52.300 --> 01:06:53.980
if that seems to work.

01:06:53.980 --> 01:06:56.350
And so therefore, as
your cells ramp up,

01:06:56.350 --> 01:07:00.550
your commissions ramp
up in line with that.

