01:13:00.020 --> 01:13:04.360
And my initial reaction was
that seems really onerous.

01:13:04.360 --> 01:13:07.190
It doesn't seem
like a great deal.

01:13:07.190 --> 01:13:11.080
But when you realize that
he's coming in at this stage,

01:13:11.080 --> 01:13:15.300
he's coming in really
as the angel investor,

01:13:15.300 --> 01:13:19.340
and by the time this all gets
done-- well, what's my example?

01:13:19.340 --> 01:13:21.250
My example actually works out.

01:13:21.250 --> 01:13:23.700
Just take a zero off of this.

