That would be $40,000 a
year, or $10,000 a quarter.

01:15:38.930 --> 01:15:41.600
Every quarter, you vest $10,000.

01:15:41.600 --> 01:15:45.170
So if you leave after two years,
you have your 80,000 shares,

01:15:45.170 --> 01:15:48.600
and you go, and they're yours.

01:15:48.600 --> 01:15:53.845
And the $80,000 that
you didn't invest--

01:15:53.845 --> 01:15:55.970
look, if you thought it
was going to be successful,

01:15:55.970 --> 01:15:57.370
you shouldn't be leaving.

01:15:57.370 --> 01:16:00.995
So you've left that,
and those are gone.

