01:16:30.580 --> 01:16:34.020
first off you have the
money to pay a CFO,

01:16:34.020 --> 01:16:36.470
and it will be money well spent.

01:16:36.470 --> 01:16:39.600
Because as I showed you, all
those rounds of financing

01:16:39.600 --> 01:16:44.340
at Reveal, I can't tell
